data.description: BASEMENT GALEN FLOOR PLAN 4 bedroom 2.5 bath. New luxury homes close to downtown! The lowest prices new single family homes in all of Atlanta! You won't get an opportunity like this again. Pricing will skyrocket, you will miss out for introductory pricing. There are NO new homes in this price range! Get in now and enjoy the increase in value. The spacious island kitchen opens to a casual breakfast area and flows effortlessly into a generous family room. Cabinet color options include gray, white and espresso. Upstairs offers a private bedroom suite with spa-like bath, plus large secondary bedrooms. And you will never be too far from home with Home Is Connected. Your new home is built with an industry leading suite of smart home products that keep you connected with the people and place you value most. Photo renderings, under construction. Basement is unfinished
